
 * we have set of starters for those applications that
 provides set of applications that can be used to
 compose a task or stream pipeline,

 * we might also deploy all those applications into kuberneties or cloud foundery

 orchestration:

 * integrating data sources, systems and applications,

 * it is all about grouping services and quickly adjust them

 * we are composing applications into task or stream based pipelines

 implementation:

 * we can deploy pipelines to kubernetes, cloud foundery,

 * we can have many instances of specific applications in that stream

 * we can also make a partitioning of our applications, but here
 we do not have to take care of indexing them in the right way,

 * using docker create images for redis, mysql, rabbitmq

